# Arduino Internship Repository

## Overview

This repository contains all daily tasks, experiments, and projects completed during the Arduino and IoT Internship.

The purpose of this repository is to maintain a structured record of:

- Arduino sketches
- Hardware documentation
- Wiring images
- Project progress

